description.en:
Hland protocol is a decentralized financial platform built on the Ethereum network to provide users with a SIMPLE & EASY profit maximizing solution AI - for Profit Maximization & Risk Minimization.
And Hland lending protocol also provides extensive AI driven risk minimization measures. Our automatic data valuation engine first filters through all the relevant data, then provides only high-quality data into the risk minimization engine to adjust relevant parameters across Hland's lending protocol.
